        "text": ".) Vulg., “deditque consilium populo, et statuit cantores domini.”",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "And that should praise the beauty of holiness.—Rather, and men praising, in holy apparel. i.e., Levitical vestments (1Chronicles 16:29; Psalm 29:2).",
