        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Praise the Lord.—Give thanks unto Jehovah The refrain of the singers. (See on 1Chronicles 16:34; 1Chronicles 16:41; 2Chronicles 5:13; 2Chronicles 7:3.) The band of Levitical minstrels were to march before the army (halûq, the armed host; Joshua 6:7).",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "bld",
            "text": "Praise the Lord.",
